[
  {
    "startTime": 0.14,
    "endTime": 4.76,
    "text": "Bruno Mars, this will surprise you that I've done this much research."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.76,
    "endTime": 6.96,
    "text": "I hear it's not your real name."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.98,
    "endTime": 7.800000000000001,
    "text": "It's not my real name."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.8,
    "endTime": 9.24,
    "text": "It's not his real name."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.6,
    "endTime": 11.48,
    "text": "You caught me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.48,
    "endTime": 13.92,
    "text": "Ok, that's all for tonight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.66,
    "endTime": 16.26,
    "text": "So what were you called?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.26,
    "endTime": 17.200000000000003,
    "text": "Peter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.2,
    "endTime": 18.599999999999998,
    "text": "So where did the Bruno come from?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.6,
    "endTime": 23.200000000000003,
    "text": "\"Bruno\"- I was a chubby baby and there was a wrestler in my dad's day named Bruno Sammartino."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.2,
    "endTime": 24.779,
    "text": "Are you familliar?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.779,
    "endTime": 26.419,
    "text": "I remember that wrestler, yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.42,
    "endTime": 31.200000000000003,
    "text": "He was a stocky guy, and I used to walk around like a little bulldog, my dad said he'd always call me Bruno Sammartino."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.2,
    "endTime": 33.68,
    "text": "\"Mars\" just kinda came joking around in the studio."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.68,
    "endTime": 34.58,
    "text": "Oh yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.18,
    "endTime": 36.96,
    "text": "Saying I'm out of this world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.92,
    "endTime": 42.800000000000004,
    "text": "What people don't realise, they might have thought we were being stupid playing Billionaire when you came on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.8,
    "endTime": 47.28,
    "text": "But, you wrote Billionaire and you've written loads of songs, apart from-"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.3,
    "endTime": 48.559999999999995,
    "text": "Yeah, quite a few this year."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.58,
    "endTime": 49.22,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.54,
    "endTime": 55.12,
    "text": "Now, call me lazy, but isn't that a much better way to go?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.12,
    "endTime": 57.4,
    "text": "Just write songs for other people?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.42,
    "endTime": 59.96,
    "text": "You make the money, you don't have to do the stupid touring."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.96,
    "endTime": 61.68,
    "text": "No, I love that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.08,
    "endTime": 64.3,
    "text": "Stupid touring now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.84,
    "endTime": 66.18,
    "text": "Go on, what other songs have you written."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.18,
    "endTime": 67.5,
    "text": "Come on, tell us, 'cause Billionaire was a huge hit, wasn't it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.5,
    "endTime": 71.28,
    "text": "I wrote Thriller, Purple Rain um- I'm joking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.3,
    "endTime": 75.72,
    "text": "Jimmy's going 'wow, that is impressive.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.7,
    "endTime": 78.82000000000001,
    "text": "Happy Birthday, that's his."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.98,
    "endTime": 80.0,
    "text": "Happy Birthday, I wrote that one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.0,
    "endTime": 82.16,
    "text": "Can we see if this is a wig?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.28,
    "endTime": 87.26,
    "text": "It's not a wig, but it's definitely been in that thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.7,
    "endTime": 90.5,
    "text": "No, I recently did a song for Cee Lo called F- You."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.5,
    "endTime": 91.0,
    "text": "I don't know if you guys heard that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.0,
    "endTime": 91.7,
    "text": "Oh my god."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.7,
    "endTime": 92.5,
    "text": "That was you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.5,
    "endTime": 93.4,
    "text": "That's a great song."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.4,
    "endTime": 95.32000000000001,
    "text": "That's amazing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.5,
    "endTime": 98.0,
    "text": "I'm obsessed with that song."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.0,
    "endTime": 99.3,
    "text": "Awesome, thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.3,
    "endTime": 103.5,
    "text": "Why would you give that song away though 'cause you're a singer and a solo artist, why would you...?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.5,
    "endTime": 109.5,
    "text": "It wasn't given away, we had a session booked with him and we started jamming and that was the song we came up with."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.5,
    "endTime": 110.5,
    "text": "Have you ever heard this song?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.5,
    "endTime": 111.0,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.0,
    "endTime": 111.8,
    "text": "What!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.8,
    "endTime": 113.17999999999999,
    "text": "It's extraordinary."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.22,
    "endTime": 114.7,
    "text": "This is a great song."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.74,
    "endTime": 119.0,
    "text": "- I'm not good on modern stuff. - If only we had someone here who could sing it..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.0,
    "endTime": 121.12,
    "text": "Come on, give us a burst."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.12,
    "endTime": 122.94,
    "text": "♪ Forget You - Cee Lo Green ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.02,
    "endTime": 130.18,
    "text": "How cool is that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.0,
    "endTime": 132.94,
    "text": "Cee Lo!"
  }
]